title: Camille Kostek, Sam Darnold Traded, and the Wingman Plus One
description:
Subscribe, rate, share, and leave a review! -Bringing a wingman as a plus 1 to a wedding -Therapists taking vacation -Would would your Barstool Sports +1 to a wedding be? -Top 5 Waters -Sam Darnold is traded from the Jets -John's Notebook -Where'd the nuns go? -Dog dreams -What's that commercial trying to pull? -Voicemails (01:39:52) Camille Kostek returns to the show! We discuss the idea of her and Gronk having a reality show, hanging out with Gisele (but not getting her number yet), and becoming the host of Wipeout! Does Gronk get jealous of John Cena? Was Tom Brady drunk at the Tampa Bay parade? All that and much more.
